    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>P. Iyanu DIRIWARI</h1>
      <p class="lead">Field Application &amp; R&amp;D Scientist • Bioanalytical Chemist • Spectroscopy &amp; Diagnostics</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#about"><i class="fa-solid fa-compass"></i> Explore my work</a>
